        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/35077347/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/35077347/" class="">第3212页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/xiaoyaojiaozi/" class=" " title="小炼师">小炼师</a>
                (我什么都不会。。。)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="35077347">
              <div class="short">
                
